reviewText: Loved it. Very interesting movie if you like independent films.
Great movie at a suberb price. I had been looking for this movie for years to complete my collection.  The acting is wonderful.

I really liked this movie. I watched it on PBS one night and now I can get my own copy. Such a sweet story and the guy who plays Floyd is super hot.
